metadata.name: Mysterious Shiningstar
metadata.description:
Oh wondrous creature, born of light and moon
Emerging from the intersection of the sun
Your wings of silver and your eyes so bright
Illuminate the world with your radiant light

You are a being of magic and mystery
A creature of otherworldly beauty
Your presence is a wonder to behold
Your grace and elegance, never to be old

You dance among the stars, soaring through the sky
A beacon of hope, a guiding light
You are a source of inspiration and delight
A blessing to all who are lucky enough to sight

Oh mysterious creature, forever we shall praise
Your beauty, your magic, your eternal rays
You are a symbol of all that is pure and true
A shining star, forever shining through
